
This tool automates downloading and installing OS images to the HiKey board.

Please note that this is work in progress! Please review the scripts before using them.

Usage:

1. Create a config file for the OS you wish to download/install
   -> refer to configs/template_* for details
   
2. Fetch the OS:
   # ./HiKeyTool.sh configs/<config.conf> fetch
   
3. Install the OS:
   # ./HiKeyTool.sh configs/<config.conf> flash

